title: 1993–94 Scottish Cup
text: The 1993–94 <a href="Scottish%20Cup">Scottish Cup</a> was the 109th staging of Scotland's most prestigious <a href="Association%20football">football</a> knockout competition. The Cup was won by <a href="Dundee%20United%20F.C.">Dundee United</a> who defeated <a href="Rangers%20F.C.">Rangers</a> in the final.
